&lt;p&gt;For over 55 years ASM has been ahead of what’s next, at the forefront of innovation and what’s technologically possible. With more than 4,500 ASMers representing 70 nationalities, our people and our advanced semiconductor devices are playing a crucial role in trends such as 5G, cloud computing, AI, and autonomous driving.  But&amp;nbsp;we’re more than just a tech company. We value diversity, inclusion and sustainability as we strive to make a positive impact on the world.&amp;nbsp; Our development programs help support your growth, shaping your future and pushing the boundaries of innovation to unleash potential.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
