&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Digital Solutions Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing Global Spares and Services organization. In this role, you will play a critical part in enabling Field Service teams with the data, knowledge, and digital tools needed to improve service efficiency, drive first-time-right outcomes, and reduce equipment installation and maintenance cycle times at customer sites.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a highly cross-functional role at the intersection of&amp;nbsp;data engineering, application development, and operational enablement, ideal for someone who enjoys solving real-world problems by integrating systems and building impactful solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
